OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777719769
OL,3,CPetrol stations in the sea and crazy
OL,4,Cprices: Errors in official fuel price
OL,5,Cdata
OL,7,FPetrol prices are higher than they
OL,8,Fhave been for years, but #13.69 a
OL,9,Flitre is ridiculous.
OL,11,FThat's one of the errors ITV News has
OL,12,Fseen in price data, as experts say the
OL,13,Fgovernment's new "fuel finder" scheme
OL,14,Fhas teething problems.
OL,16,FThe government claims its new data
OL,17,Fcould save an average driver #40 a
OL,18,Fyear and that 95% of petrol stations
OL,19,Fhave already signed up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777719769
OL,3,CPetrol stations in the sea and crazy
OL,4,Cprices: Errors in official fuel price
OL,5,Cdata
OL,7,FBut mistakes include one UK forecourt
OL,8,Fshown as being in the south Atlantic
OL,9,FOcean, and forecourts listed offering
OL,10,Fa litre of fuel for around 2p.
OL,12,FTransport expert Hugo Griffiths from
OL,13,FForecourt Trader told ITV News: "You
OL,14,Fare able to buy petrol for as little
OL,15,Fas 1.5p a litre if the system is to be
OL,16,Fbelieved - or if you prefer, you can
OL,17,Fgo and buy petrol for #15 a litre!
OL,26,@uD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
