OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777719769
OL,3,CPetrol stations in the sea and crazy
OL,4,Cprices: Errors in official fuel price
OL,5,Cdata
OL,7,F"All of these errors are likely the
OL,8,Fresult of individual forecourt
OL,9,Foperators miskeying and getting the
OL,10,Fdecimal point in the wrong place."
OL,12,FFriday, May 1, is the first day
OL,13,Fofficials are enforcing this new UK-
OL,14,Fwide fuel price reporting system.
OL,16,FAll of the UK's approximately 8,500
OL,17,Fpetrol forecourts must now report
OL,18,Fprice changes within 30 minutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
