OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777719769
OL,3,CPetrol stations in the sea and crazy
OL,4,Cprices: Errors in official fuel price
OL,5,Cdata
OL,7,FThe data is then made public for
OL,8,Fdrivers to access via a variety of
OL,9,Fapps and digital tools, such as in-car
OL,10,Fmap and navigation systems.
OL,12,FMotoring expert Jade Tilbury from
OL,13,FWebuyanycar.com told ITV News the core
OL,14,Fprice information is accurate and the
OL,15,Fnew scheme could turbocharge drivers'
OL,16,Fability to shop around.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
