OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1777719769
OL,3,CPetrol stations in the sea and crazy
OL,4,Cprices: Errors in official fuel price
OL,5,Cdata
OL,7,F"It gives access to up-to-date price
OL,8,Fcomparisons, no matter what fuel type
OL,9,Fand wherever you are in the country.
OL,10,FSo being able to utilise that means
OL,11,Feven the difference of 1p or 2p a
OL,12,Flitre over the course of a few weeks
OL,13,For a few months will make a huge
OL,14,Fdifference to motorists," she said.
OL,16,FThe government told us the scheme will
OL,17,Fhelp in this cost of living crisis,
OL,18,Fand the data team behind the system
OL,19,Fsays it works hard to identify and
OL,20,Fcorrect any inconsistencies.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
